*   ## **_TBS CHAMPIONSHIP: MERCEDES MONE DEF. NYLA ROSE_**
    

Post match, Britt Baker disguised as Sting attacks Mercedes before Mercedes RUNS as fast as she can and security catches Britt

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a7aab45b-c154-49c1-a673-bfbbfe00f435/20240717_183555.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4f0ba2b5-80c8-4ebe-a491-7a9e8c7a8e8f/20240717_184739.jpg?format=original)

Mariah May explains that she was willing to ride this relationship with Toni Storm out until it was time to take her out back and get rid of her. Until she saw Wembley Stadium.

Mariah says Toni Storm’s greatest performance was when she got down on her knees and BLED for Mariah May.

Toni Storm was so blinded by her superstardom she didn't realize she was giving it all away.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a4804b95-b7c6-4513-b355-57bd6d014dfd/20240717_184743.jpg?format=original)

