![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8cf2d2b7-93f7-42ed-9a9e-d18b6fda490b/20240717_215045.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_AEW CHAMPION SWERVE STRICKLAND DEF. CONTINENTAL CHAMPION KAZUCHIKA OKADA BY DQ_**
    

Swerve and Okada give us a taste of a potential match down the line but it ends after about 12 minutes. The Elite jump Swerve which leads to Team AEW running out and that brings out Hangman Page.

Hangman and Swerve don't get to touch each other tho as the brawl engulfs them both. Darby Allen drops down from the rafters to join Team AEW in this brawl and next week at Blood and Guts.